      <title>IRC 称非洲各地冲突和政变以惊人的速度上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/conflict-coups-rising-at-alarming-rate-across-africa-irc-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际救援委员会表示，非洲的冲突、政变和贫困正在以惊人的速度上升，过去十年里，非洲武装团体的数量增加了一倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/conflict-coups-rising-at-alarming-rate-across-africa-irc-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:41:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰公共交通因罢工而陷入停顿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/finland-s-public-transport-grinds-to-halt-as-strikes-hit-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一波 24 小时罢工浪潮袭击了这个北欧国家，芬兰的公共交通暂停，一些发电厂关闭，港口出口停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/finland-s-public-transport-grinds-to-halt-as-strikes-hit-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯袭击后，焦虑和武装的以色列发生了转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/israelis-buy-guns-after-hamas-attack-transformed-society</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期可以自由流浪的以色列儿童现在经常有人陪伴。枪支许可证申请量增加了八倍。自卫课程报名人数超额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/israelis-buy-guns-after-hamas-attack-transformed-society</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
